interactableTiles.message: Do you ever notice these buildings are bigger on the inside?#I notice. I notice every day...
It usually takes the single jumpers a few attempts to get up here.#I like to watch. It's funny.

I'm pretty sure this ladder hasn't been used at all recently. Or... ever.#These people seem to be pretty into the whole jumping thing. I guess I should play along.#Plus, I've no way of knowing that this can actually hold the weight of a human...

You need to talk to the mayor of Yarnberg?#Well, the town hall here is where he is most of the time.#Jeff's a pretty informal guy, though. And he's never been keen on single jumpers. But he runs the place pretty well, so...
